00:48:37,130 --> 00:48:40,133
ICH BIN
 THE AMERICANKOMMANDANT.

623
00:48:40,133 --> 00:48:42,135
PERHAPS YOU
UNDERSTAND ENGLISH.

624
00:48:42,135 --> 00:48:45,138
BACK AT THE CAMP,
THE MEN CHOSE ME--
GO BACK IN LINE.

625
00:48:45,138 --> 00:48:49,643
I WAS TOLD
TO TAKE CHARGE.
[ Speaking German ]

626
00:48:49,643 --> 00:48:53,146
OKAY, FELLAS.
MOVE OUT.  MOVE OUT.

627
00:51:43,066 --> 00:51:45,569
[ Woman Laughing ]

628
00:51:52,075 --> 00:51:56,079
???? [ Stops ]
[ Speaking German ]

629
00:52:07,591 --> 00:52:12,078
[ Val ]
DON'T FOOL AROUND
WITH ANY OO-LA-LAS.

630
00:52:12,078 --> 00:52:14,581
[ Billy ]  HOW CAN I CHEAT
WITH YOUR OLD MAN AROUND ?

631
00:52:15,081 --> 00:52:17,083
[ Lionel ]
THAT WON'T BE SO HARD.
WE JUST MAKE AN AGREEMENT.

632
00:52:17,551 --> 00:52:20,053
YOU DON'T TALK,
AND I DON'T TALK.
DADDY, SHAME ON YOU !

633
00:52:20,554 --> 00:52:23,056
[ Laughs ]
HEY, COME ON, BILLY.
WE'RE ON OUR WAY.

634
00:52:23,473 --> 00:52:26,810
- BYE-BYE, BARB.
- BYE, VAL.
- HAVE A GOOD TIME.

635
00:52:26,810 --> 00:52:31,398
BYE, SWEETHEART.
HAVE A GOOD TIME.  BYE.
BYE, HON.  OKAY.

636
00:52:31,398 --> 00:52:33,817
[ Crowd Calling Farewells ]

637
00:52:34,217 --> 00:52:36,620
BYE.

638
00:52:44,628 --> 00:52:46,630
I KNOW THERE'S
GONNA BE MEETINGS,

639
00:52:46,630 --> 00:52:49,833
BUT I REALLY MOSTLY
WANT YOU TO ENJOY YOURSELF.

640
00:52:49,833 --> 00:52:53,436
BY GOD, YOU DESERVE IT.
YOU REALLY DO.

641
00:52:53,436 --> 00:52:55,839
WANT ME TO TELL YOU
A SECRET, HUH ?

642
00:52:55,839 --> 00:52:58,642
I WOULDN'T TELL ANYBODY THIS,
OF COURSE, BUT...

643
00:52:58,642 --> 00:53:03,046
WHEN VALENCIA BROUGHT YOU HOME
AND WANTED TO MARRY YOU, TO TELL
YOU THE HONEST-TO-GOD TRUTH,

644
00:53:03,046 --> 00:53:05,448
I THOUGHT SHE'D BROUGHT HOME
A FIRST-CLASS LOSER !

645
00:53:05,849 --> 00:53:08,251
[ Plane Engines Whirring ]
I REALLY THOUGHT THAT.
BUT YOU PROVED ME WRONG.

646
00:53:08,251 --> 00:53:11,221
[ Whirring Grows Louder ]
I'M THE FIRST
TO ADMIT IT.

647
00:53:11,221 --> 00:53:13,723
YOU PROVED
OLD LIONEL WRONG.

648
00:53:13,723 --> 00:53:16,610
[ Lionel Continues,
  Indistinct ]

649
00:53:16,610 --> 00:53:18,612
DAD ?

650
00:53:27,103 --> 00:53:29,005
FINE FAMILY MAN,
AND I'M--

651
00:53:42,669 --> 00:53:45,872
THE PLANE'S GONNA CRASH.
[ Laughs ]
OH, COME ON, BILLY-BOY !

652
00:53:46,273 --> 00:53:48,425
IN 25 MINUTES,
THE WHOLE THING CRACKS UP.

653
00:53:48,425 --> 00:53:50,844
YOU CAN'T GET OUT
OF YOUR SEAT !

654
00:53:52,596 --> 00:53:54,764
STOP THE PLANE.
NO ONE'S ALLOWED
IN THE COCKPIT, SIR.

655
00:53:54,764 --> 00:53:58,935
IT'S GONNA CRASH.  I ORGANIZED
THIS CHARTER; I'M RESPONSIBLE--
DO YOU WANT TO BE REMOVED ?

656
00:53:58,935 --> 00:54:01,938
BUT YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND !
WE'VE GOT OUR CLEARANCE
FOR THE TAKEOFF.

657
00:54:01,938 --> 00:54:05,942
EVERYTHING'S GOING TO BE ALL
RIGHT.  LEAVE THE DRIVING TO US.

658
00:54:05,942 --> 00:54:09,663
LOUSY, DRUNK, SON OF A BITCH !
GOD, I HATE
THESE CHARTER FLIGHTS.

659
00:54:21,508 --> 00:54:25,178
?? OH, THERE'S A CHANGE
  IN THE WEATHER, THERE'S
  A CHANGE IN THE SCENE ??

660
00:54:25,178 --> 00:54:29,182
?? BUM, BUM, BUM, BUM
  SO FROM NOW ON THERE'LL
  BE A CHANGE IN ME ??

661
00:54:29,182 --> 00:54:32,385
?? BUM, BUM
  MY WALK WILL BE DIFFERENT
  MY TALK AND MY NAME ??

662
00:54:32,385 --> 00:54:34,387
?? BUM, BUM, BUM, BUM
  NOTHIN' ABOUT ME ??

663
00:54:34,387 --> 00:54:36,539
?? WILL BE THE SAME ??
YOU FEEL ALL RIGHT ?

664
00:54:36,539 --> 00:54:41,344
THAT SURE WAS A LOUSY JOKE
YOU PULLED BACK THERE
ABOUT THE PLANE CRASHING.

665
00:54:41,344 --> 00:54:43,747
I'M SORRY, DAD.
FORGET IT.

666
00:54:44,197 --> 00:54:46,283
STEWARDESS,
BRING THIS YOUNG FELLA
ANOTHER DRINK !

667
00:54:46,283 --> 00:54:50,320
?? BUM, BUM, BUM, BUM
  THERE'LL BE SOME CHANGES ??

668
00:54:50,320 --> 00:54:54,491
?? MADE TODAY ????

669
00:54:54,491 --> 00:54:58,995
[ Explosion ]

670
00:54:58,995 --> 00:55:02,165
[ Engines Whining ]

671
00:55:07,454 --> 00:55:10,140
[ Train Rumbling ]
[ Bell Clangs ]

672
00:55:16,096 --> 00:55:20,400
[ Traffic Noises,
  Pedestrians Speaking German ]

673
00:55:23,670 --> 00:55:28,241
SCHLACHTHOF-FUNF.
THIS IS SCHLACHTHOF-FUNF.

674
00:55:28,241 --> 00:55:30,744
FUNFIS ENGLISH FIVE.

675
00:55:30,744 --> 00:55:34,247
SCHLACHTIS SLAUGHTER.
HOFIS HOUSE.

676
00:55:34,247 --> 00:55:38,752
SCHLACHTHOF-FUNF:
SLAUGHTERHOUSE-FIVE.

677
00:55:38,752 --> 00:55:43,256
NO, THE RULES OF THE GENEVA
CONVENTION PROHIBIT--
HALTES MAL !  HALTES MAL !

678
00:55:43,256 --> 00:55:46,760
YOU MUST LEARN THE ADDRESS
FOR YOUR OWN WELL-BEING.

679
00:55:47,260 --> 00:55:50,764
IN EVENT OF EMERGENCY,
YOU WILL SAY SCHLACHTHOF-FUNF.

680
00:55:50,764 --> 00:55:53,266
SAY IT, PLEASE.  SCHLACHT.
[ Prisoners ]
SCHLACHT.

681
00:55:53,266 --> 00:55:56,770
- HOF.
- HOF.

682
00:55:56,770 --> 00:55:58,772
- FUNF !
- FUNF.

683
00:55:59,272 --> 00:56:04,728
- SCHLACHTHOF-FUNF.
- SCHLACHTHOF-FUNF.

684
00:56:04,728 --> 00:56:07,063
SCHLACHTHOF-FUNF.

685
00:56:22,962 --> 00:56:24,464
[ Billy ]
FUNF.

686
00:56:26,549 --> 00:56:30,153
SCHLACHT... HOF...

687
00:56:30,153 --> 00:56:32,155
FUNF.

688
00:56:35,759 --> 00:56:37,761
SCHLACHT...

689
00:56:37,761 --> 00:56:40,563
HOF.

690
00:56:40,563 --> 00:56:43,983
SCHLACHTHOF-FUNF.

691
00:56:44,484 --> 00:56:47,487
SCHLACHTHOF-FUNF.

692
00:56:48,888 --> 00:56:51,975
HOF... FUNF.

693
00:56:51,975 --> 00:56:54,444
SCHLACHTHOF-FUNF.

694
00:56:55,929 --> 00:56:58,548
[ Tires Squealing ]

695
00:56:59,749 --> 00:57:02,719
I'M COMING, BILLY !
 I'M COMING !

696
00:57:05,255 --> 00:57:09,809
- [ Whines ]
- [ Tires Screeching ]

697
00:57:14,230 --> 00:57:17,350
[ Sobbing ]
I'M COMING TO YOU !

698
00:57:19,719 --> 00:57:21,721
[ Honking ]

699
00:57:24,274 --> 00:57:26,676
[ Honking ]
[ Tires Screech ]

700
00:57:36,636 --> 00:57:40,640
FOR GOD'S SAKES, LADY !
WHY'D YOU JAM ON YOUR BRAKES ?
LOOK WHAT YOU'VE DONE !

701
00:57:40,640 --> 00:57:43,443
[ Wailing ]
MY BILLY FELL OUT
OF A PLANE !

702
00:57:43,843 --> 00:57:47,046
I WAS GOING TO THE HOSPITAL !
 I MISSED MY ENTRANCE !

703
00:57:47,046 --> 00:57:50,400
I'LL DRIVE YOU THERE.
NO !  IT'S
IN VERMONT, STUPID !

704
00:57:50,400 --> 00:57:52,852
[ Sobbing ]
BILLY.

705
00:57:52,852 --> 00:57:55,788
HEY, LET ME
SEE YOUR LICENSE !
I HAVEN'T GOT TIME !

706
00:57:55,788 --> 00:57:59,058
YOU CAN'T LEAVE THE SCENE
OF AN ACCIDENT, LADY !

707
00:58:00,260 --> 00:58:03,363
YOUR EXHAUST
IS SHOT TO HELL !
DAMN IT, LADY !

708
00:58:03,363 --> 00:58:07,851
- YOU'RE GOIN'
  THE WRONG WAY !
-[ Car Honking ]

709
00:58:20,897 --> 00:58:23,283
GET OUT OF THE WAY !

710
00:58:24,784 --> 00:58:26,786
GODDAMN !
GET OUTTA THE WAY !
[ Truck Honking ]

711
00:58:31,925 --> 00:58:35,562
FIRST SHE BACKED INTO ME.  THEN
SHE WENT THE WRONG WAY AND--
[ Tires Squealing ]

712
00:58:36,763 --> 00:58:38,364
OH, MY GOD,
HERE SHE COMES AGAIN.

713
00:58:38,848 --> 00:58:40,850
[ Car Rattling ]

714
00:58:48,641 --> 00:58:51,494
[ Siren Wailing ]

715
00:58:56,316 --> 00:58:59,919
[ Siren Continues ]

716
00:59:06,960 --> 00:59:10,797
I'M COMING TO YOU,
BILLY.  I'M COMING !

717
00:59:12,298 --> 00:59:14,250
-SWEETHEART.  HONEY ?
- HMM.

718
00:59:14,250 --> 00:59:17,253
HUH ?  WHAT ?
WAKE UP, WAKE UP.
 WAKE UP !

719
00:59:17,253 --> 00:59:19,255
WHAT ?

720
00:59:21,257 --> 00:59:24,260
HERE.
WHAT IS IT ?

721
00:59:26,262 --> 00:59:29,766
[ Gasps ]
BILLY !  WHAT IS IT ?

722
00:59:29,766 --> 00:59:32,435
FOLLOW IT AND FIND OUT.
BILLY !

723
00:59:32,435 --> 00:59:36,039
COME ON.
OH, BILLY.  YOU'RE
ALWAYS UP TO SOMETHING.

724
00:59:36,039 --> 00:59:38,841
YOU'RE WONDERFUL.
THANK YOU.  BEAUTIFUL !

725
00:59:39,242 --> 00:59:43,646
BUT DID YOU MAKE THIS ?
NEVER MIND THE BOW.
FOLLOW THE YELLOW-BRICK ROAD.

726
00:59:43,646 --> 00:59:45,648
[ Squealing ]
FOLLOW THE YELLOW-BRICK ROAD !

727
00:59:45,648 --> 00:59:48,518
[ Laughs ]

728
00:59:48,518 --> 00:59:52,505
FOLLOW THE YELLOW-BRICK ROAD !
OH, BILLY !
COME ON.  FOLLOW IT.

729
00:59:52,505 --> 00:59:55,008
[ Squeals ]
BILLY !

730
00:59:55,008 --> 00:59:57,176
COME ON, MAMA !  FOLLOW.

731
00:59:57,677 --> 00:59:59,178
FOLLOW THE YELLOW-BRICK ROAD !

732
00:59:59,679 --> 01:00:02,682
[ Barbara ]
MOM !  COME ON DOWN, MOM.
DID YOU REALLY MAKE THIS BOW ?

733
01:00:02,682 --> 01:00:05,184
NEVER MIND.
[ Barbara ]
MOM !  HURRY !

734
01:00:05,685 --> 01:00:08,187
I'M COMING.
[ Laughs ]
ROBERT !

735
01:00:08,187 --> 01:00:11,691
[ Barbara ]
MOM, HURRY.

736
01:00:11,691 --> 01:00:15,695
BILLY !  BILLY,
I CAN'T GO OUT LIKE THIS.

737
01:00:15,695 --> 01:00:18,197
OF COURSE YOU CAN.
FOLLOW THE GOLDEN THREAD.

738
01:00:18,197 --> 01:00:20,366
[ Gasps ]

739
01:00:20,366 --> 01:00:23,569
A CADILLAC !
OH, BILLY !

740
01:00:23,569 --> 01:00:27,173
HAPPY BIRTHDAY, HON.
HAPPY BIRTHDAY, MOM !

741
01:00:29,575 --> 01:00:31,577
A CADILLAC !
 A WHITE CADILLAC !

742
01:00:31,978 --> 01:00:35,181
IT'S WHAT I'VE
ALWAYS WANTED !
[ Squeals, Laughs ]

743
01:00:35,581 --> 01:00:37,183
COME ON, ROBERT !

744
01:00:37,583 --> 01:00:39,585
I'VE ALWAYS WANTED
A WHITE CADILLAC !

745
01:00:39,585 --> 01:00:43,990
OH, BILLY.
 OH, SWEETHEART.
AND NOW YOU'VE GOT IT.

746
01:00:43,990 --> 01:00:47,193
OH, IT'S A LITTLE TIGHT.
YOU CAN ADJUST THE SEAT
WITH THIS, SEE ?

747
01:00:47,193 --> 01:00:49,595
OH, NO, NO !
THAT'S TOO TIGHT !
OR BACKWARD.

748
01:00:49,595 --> 01:00:51,998
YOU CAN MAKE IT GO UP--
OH, NO !
IT'S SQUISHING ME !

749
01:00:52,398 --> 01:00:55,201
OR DOWN.
[ Giggling ]
IT'S WONDERFUL !

750
01:00:55,201 --> 01:01:00,406
I'M GONNA LOSE WEIGHT !
OH, I'M REALLY GONNA, BILLY.
I LOVE YOU.  I LOVE YOU.

751
01:01:00,406 --> 01:01:03,242
[ Horn Honks ]

752
01:01:03,242 --> 01:01:05,328
[ Car Rattling ]

753
01:01:18,541 --> 01:01:20,293
GET THE STRETCHER !  QUICK !

754
01:01:48,705 --> 01:01:51,708
-[ Doctor ]  WAS HE ALERT
 IN THE EMERGENCY ROOM ?
-[ Man ]  NO, NOT VERY.

755
01:01:51,708 --> 01:01:54,377
HIS RIGHT EYE WAS DILATING
AND HIS BLOOD PRESSURE WAS UP.

756
01:01:54,377 --> 01:01:56,379
HE SEEMED PRETTY DROWSY.

757
01:01:56,379 --> 01:01:58,781
[ Woman ]
HE'S SHAVED
AND PREPPED, DOCTOR.

758
01:01:58,781 --> 01:02:01,834
LET'S GET THE PRESSURE OFF.
ARE THE INSTRUMENTS READY ?
YES, DOCTOR.

759
01:02:04,303 --> 01:02:08,808
BETTER GET IN QUICKLY, BILL.
HIS RIGHT PUPIL NO LONGER
REACTS TO LIGHT.

760
01:02:08,808 --> 01:02:10,810
SCALPEL.

761
01:02:10,810 --> 01:02:15,314
[ Respirator Pumping ]

762
01:02:19,819 --> 01:02:21,320
[ Doctor ]
CAUTERY.

763
01:02:23,823 --> 01:02:26,325
[ Pumping Continues ]

764
01:02:27,827 --> 01:02:31,831
ELECTRIC BURR.

765
01:02:31,831 --> 01:02:34,333
[ Electric Burr Buzzing ]

766
01:02:34,333 --> 01:02:36,335
LET ME HAVE SOME SALINE.

767
01:02:36,335 --> 01:02:41,841
EACH DAY, YOU WILL RECITE
YOUR NUMBER SO WE'LL KNOW
HOW MANY MEN ARE HERE.

768
01:02:41,841 --> 01:02:45,845
THERE'LL BE NO TALKIN'
TO GERMANS UNLESS TALKED TO.

769
01:02:45,845 --> 01:02:48,347
WHEN THE WAR IS OVER,
WE'LL TALK.

770
01:02:48,347 --> 01:02:52,852
[ Respirator Pumping ]
LET'S MAKE ANOTHER
BURR HOLE RIGHT HERE.

771
01:02:52,852 --> 01:02:56,355
EACH DAY, YOU WILL BE GIVEN
A WORKING ASSIGNMENT...

772
01:02:56,355 --> 01:02:59,358
FOR FACTORY,
CLEANING OR MAIL.

773
01:02:59,358 --> 01:03:01,861
BUT THERE IS NOT GOING TO BE
ANY TALKING TO GERMAN.

774
01:03:02,361 --> 01:03:05,364
WHEN YOU TALK, YOU TALK
TO YOUR GUARDS ONLY.

775
01:03:05,364 --> 01:03:08,568
[ Bleeping ]
[ Man ]
BLOOD PRESSURE IS FALLING OFF.

776
01:03:09,986 --> 01:03:13,489
EINS, ZWEI !
 EINS, ZWEI !  EINS, ZWEI !

777
01:03:18,995 --> 01:03:22,999
[ Pumping Continues ]

778
01:03:27,920 --> 01:03:30,423
[ No Audible Dialogue ]

779
01:03:34,427 --> 01:03:36,379
[ Doctor ]
WHAT ARE YOU GIVING HIM ?

780
01:03:36,379 --> 01:03:38,815
[ Anesthetist ]
I'M STILL GIVING HIM D5W.

781
01:03:38,815 --> 01:03:42,018
[ Heart Monitor
  Bleeping ]
[ No Audible Dialogue ]

782
01:03:42,435 --> 01:03:44,937
[ Speaking German ]

783
01:03:44,937 --> 01:03:47,440
[ Respirator Pumping,
  Bleeping Continues ]

784
01:03:49,442 --> 01:03:51,477
[ Bleeping Stops ]

785
01:03:59,502 --> 01:04:02,672
[ Anesthetist ]
IT LOOKS LIKE THE PRESSURE'S
COMING UP NOW.

786
01:04:02,672 --> 01:04:04,991
LET'S SEE HOW WE DO IN THE
NEXT FIVE OR TEN MINUTES.

787
01:04:05,391 --> 01:04:07,393
[ Bleeping Resumes ]

788
01:04:22,024 --> 01:04:24,277
MRS. SHAW ?

789
01:04:24,277 --> 01:04:26,779
I'M DOCTOR ELLENBOGEN.
YOUR FATHER'S GONNA BE
ALL RIGHT.

790
01:04:27,280 --> 01:04:30,967
IT WAS VERY DIFFICULT,
BUT HE CAME THROUGH
IN GOOD SHAPE.

791
01:04:31,367 --> 01:04:33,653
STANLEY, HE'S GONNA
BE ALL RIGHT !

792
01:04:33,653 --> 01:04:36,656
WONDERFUL.
DID YOU FIND MOTHER ?

793
01:04:37,156 --> 01:04:40,443
WELL, IT--
IT'S CRAZY, BARBARA.
I-- I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

794
01:04:40,443 --> 01:04:43,246
WHAT'S CRAZY, STANLEY ?
WHERE'S MAMA ?

795
01:04:43,246 --> 01:04:45,715
COME ON, HONEY.
L-LET'S SIT DOWN.

796
01:04:48,217 --> 01:04:52,722
LISTEN.  I THINK WE'LL TAKE CARE
OF YOUR FATHER 'TIL HE'S ABLE
TO TAKE CARE OF HIMSELF.

797
01:04:52,722 --> 01:04:54,724
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT ?

798
01:04:54,724 --> 01:04:57,226
WELL, I LOOKED ALL OVER
FOR YOUR MOM,

799
01:04:57,727 --> 01:04:59,729
AND THEN I ASKED
ONE OF THE NURSES.

800
01:04:59,729 --> 01:05:02,231
AND THEY SAID THAT--

801
01:05:02,231 --> 01:05:05,735
THAT SHE DIED ABOUT
THREE HOURS AGO.

802
01:05:05,735 --> 01:05:09,238
SO I HAD TO FIND OUT
IF IT WAS THE RIGHT ONE.

803
01:05:09,238 --> 01:05:11,741
AND IT WAS.

804
01:05:11,741 --> 01:05:13,743
SHE WAS.

805
01:05:17,747 --> 01:05:20,750
HOW ?
I DON'T KNOW, UH--

806
01:05:22,251 --> 01:05:24,253
SHE HAD SOME KIND OF
ACCIDENT WITH THE CAR...

807
01:05:24,253 --> 01:05:27,757
AND GOT CARBON MONOXIDE
POISONING.

808
01:05:29,759 --> 01:05:31,761
BUT SHE DRIVES A CADILLAC !

809
01:05:31,761 --> 01:05:34,764
HONEY, I DON'T KNOW.
THAT'S WHAT THEY TOLD ME.

810
01:05:38,768 --> 01:05:41,270
OH, GOD.

811
01:05:41,270 --> 01:05:43,773
I KNOW.  I KNOW.

812
01:05:45,257 --> 01:05:48,728
[ Door Opens ]
[ Woman ]
HI, DARLING.  HOW YOU FEELING ?

813
01:05:48,728 --> 01:05:52,231
DIRTY SONS OF BITCHES.
BUREAUCRATIC BASTARDS.

814
01:05:52,231 --> 01:05:55,234
THEY HAVE THE AUDACITY TO PUT ME
IN A ROOM WITH A BASKET CASE.

815
01:05:55,234 --> 01:05:58,738
-THEY JUST DON'T HAVE
  A PRIVATE ROOM, SWEETHEART.
- WELL, I DON'T KNOW--

816
01:05:58,738 --> 01:06:00,740
GODDAMN IT, LILY !

817
01:06:00,740 --> 01:06:05,745
I'M GONNA PEPPER YOUR
RADCLIFFE ASS WITH BUCKSHOT
IF I CATCH YOU SMOKING AGAIN !

818
01:06:05,745 --> 01:06:09,248
YOU BETTER STAY IN CONDITION
TO KEEP UP WITH B.C. RUMFOORD.

819
01:06:09,248 --> 01:06:13,252
- [ Chuckles ]
- YOU GUYS GO ON WITHOUT ME.
  I'LL BE ALL RIGHT.

820
01:06:13,252 --> 01:06:16,255
CHRIST.  ALL HE DOES
IN HIS SLEEP...

821
01:06:16,255 --> 01:06:18,758
IS QUIT AND SURRENDER
AND APOLOGIZE.

822
01:06:18,758 --> 01:06:23,262
SHOOT.  I COULD CARVE
A BETTER MAN OUT OF A BANANA.
[ Chuckles ]

823
01:06:23,262 --> 01:06:25,264
[ Sighs ]
DID YOU BRING ME THOSE
BOOKS FROM WIDENER ?

824
01:06:25,264 --> 01:06:29,769
THE BOYS AT THEHARVARD CRIMSON
HAVE A BEAUTIFUL BIT ABOUT YOU.
OH ?

825
01:06:29,769 --> 01:06:33,773
THEY CALL YOU THE RED BARON
OF MILITARY HISTORY...
[ Laughing ]

826
01:06:33,773 --> 01:06:37,777
AND WANT YOU
TO GET WELL SOON.

827
01:06:37,777 --> 01:06:39,779
THOSE LITTLE BASTARDS !

828
01:06:39,779 --> 01:06:43,282
THE TRUMAN STATEMENT
ABOUT HIROSHIMA IS IN HERE,

829
01:06:43,282 --> 01:06:46,285
AND THOSE EIGHT
ARMY AIR FORCE DOCUMENTS.

830
01:06:46,285 --> 01:06:48,287
OH, YEAH.

831
01:06:48,287 --> 01:06:52,258
AND THE IRVING BOOK
ON DRESDEN.
I WAS THERE.

832
01:06:52,258 --> 01:06:56,262
HONEY, WHY DID THEY KEEP DRESDEN
A SECRET FOR SO LONG ?

833
01:06:56,262 --> 01:06:58,764
OH, HELL.  FOR FEAR
A LOT OF BLEEDING HEARTS...

834
01:06:58,764 --> 01:07:01,267
WOULD SAY BOMBING IT
WAS A CHICKEN SHIT THING TO DO.

835
01:07:01,267 --> 01:07:04,770
MY BOOK'S GONNA LAY IT
ON THE LINE, SWEETHEART.

836
01:07:04,770 --> 01:07:09,275
NOBODY'S GONNA WEEP
AND WAIL OVER DRESDEN
AFTER THEY READ MY BOOK.

837
01:07:09,275 --> 01:07:12,778
I WAS THERE.

838
01:07:12,778 --> 01:07:15,781
WHAT'S HE SAYING ?
HE SAID HE WAS THERE.

839
01:07:16,282 --> 01:07:18,284
SAYS HE WAS WHERE ?

840
01:07:18,284 --> 01:07:22,788
DRESDEN.
AT DRESDEN, B.C. !

841
01:07:27,293 --> 01:07:30,296
THE HELL WITH HIM.
LET HIM WRITE HIS OWN BOOK.

842
01:07:34,800 --> 01:07:39,605
[ Seagulls Calling ]

843
01:07:43,059 --> 01:07:48,064
[ Church Bells Tolling ]

844
01:08:48,190 --> 01:08:50,659
[ Billy ]
SCHLACHTHOF-FUNF.

845
01:08:52,044 --> 01:08:54,497
[ Rumfoord ]
WHAT THE HELL IS HE SAYING NOW ?

846
01:08:54,497 --> 01:08:57,867
[ Billy ]
ICH BIN AMERIKANISCHE SOLDAT.

847
01:08:57,867 --> 01:08:59,835
DRESDEN.

848
01:09:03,839 --> 01:09:06,842
SCHLACHTHOF-FUNF.
YOU WANNA KNOW
SOMETHING ?

849
01:09:06,842 --> 01:09:10,846
WE DIDN'T START THE LAST WAR;
THE NAZIS DID.

850
01:09:10,846 --> 01:09:13,349
AND 135,000 PEOPLE
DYING IN DRESDEN...

851
01:09:13,349 --> 01:09:18,854
DOES NOT SEEM SO VERY MUCH WHEN
PUT AGAINST OVER FIVE MILLION 
ALLIES WHO HAD TO DIE !

852
01:09:18,854 --> 01:09:21,857
AND YOU JUST MIGHT REMEMBER THAT
WHEN WE WERE BOMBING DRESDEN,

853
01:09:21,857 --> 01:09:25,361
THE GERMANS WERE SENDING V-1
AND V-2 ROCKETS INTO LONDON,

854
01:09:25,361 --> 01:09:28,113
KILLING MEN, WOMEN AND CHILDREN.

855
01:09:28,113 --> 01:09:31,116
[ Lily ]
DON'T GET SO UPTIGHT.
JESUS !

856
01:09:31,617 --> 01:09:36,121
IT GIVES ME A PAIN:  WEEPING
OVER DRESDEN AND NOT GIVE A DAMN
ABOUT OUR OWN LOSSES !

857
01:09:36,121 --> 01:09:39,625
HEY, WHAT ABOUT COVENTRY ?
WHAT ABOUT ROTTERDAM ?

858
01:09:39,625 --> 01:09:42,628
WHAT ABOUT THE EXTERMINATION
CAMPS THE GERMANS WERE RUNNING ?

859
01:09:42,628 --> 01:09:45,130
GASSING, MAIMINGS ?

860
01:09:46,131 --> 01:09:49,852
[ Children Chattering ]

861
01:09:59,195 --> 01:10:01,280
[ Hooting, Hollering ]

862
01:10:09,788 --> 01:10:13,792
[ Prisoners Chattering,
  Griping ]

863
01:10:20,299 --> 01:10:22,301
I WANT YOUR ATTENTION.

864
01:10:36,815 --> 01:10:38,817
[ Chuckling ]

865
01:10:38,817 --> 01:10:41,820
ATTENTION, PLEASE.
YOU ARE HAVING A VISITOR.

866
01:10:41,820 --> 01:10:44,823
HOWARD CAMPBELL, JUNIOR.

867
01:10:44,823 --> 01:10:48,827
I HAVE JUST COME BACK
FROM THE RUSSIAN FRONT,
SO I'LL MAKE IT SHORT.

868
01:10:48,827 --> 01:10:52,197
I KNOW HOW HUNGRY YOU ARE.
FOOD'S NOT MUCH THOUGH, IS IT ?

869
01:10:52,197 --> 01:10:55,584
FOOD'S TERRIFIC !
ALMOST AS NEAT AS YOUR OUTFIT !
[ Laughs ]

870
01:10:56,001 --> 01:10:58,404
MEN, I HAVE
A PROPOSITION
FOR YOU.

871
01:10:58,404 --> 01:11:02,424
HOW WOULD YOU LIKE TO
COME BACK TO AMERICA
AFTER THIS WAR AS HEROES ?

872
01:11:02,424 --> 01:11:04,927
GREAT, AS LONG AS I COULD
WEAR THAT FAG OUTFIT !

873
01:11:04,927 --> 01:11:08,931
-[ Scattered Chuckles ]
- [ Laughing ]

874
01:11:10,933 --> 01:11:13,435
[ Clears Throat ]

875
01:11:15,921 --> 01:11:20,025
SINCE YOU'RE SO INTERESTED
IN MY OUTFIT, I'LL TELL YOU
WHAT IT'S ABOUT.

876
01:11:20,025 --> 01:11:23,028
BLUE IS FOR THE AMERICAN SKY.

877
01:11:23,028 --> 01:11:25,531
WHITE IS FOR THE RACE THAT
PIONEERED THAT CONTINENT,

878
01:11:25,531 --> 01:11:30,536
CLEARED THE FORESTS,
DRAINED THE SWAMPS, BUILT
THE ROADS AND THE BRIDGES.

879
01:11:30,536 --> 01:11:33,038
AND THE RED IS FOR THE BLOOD
OF FINE AMERICAN BOYS...

880
01:11:33,038 --> 01:11:36,041
THAT'S BEEN SHED
IN DEFENSE OF YOUR FREEDOM.

881
01:11:36,041 --> 01:11:38,043
[ Prisoners Muttering ]

882
01:11:38,043 --> 01:11:42,047
I DON'T SEE YOU SHEDDING
ANY BLOOD, CAMPBELL.

883
01:11:42,047 --> 01:11:45,050
YOU ALL KNOW THAT COMMUNISM
IS OUT TO ENSLAVE THE WORLD.

884
01:11:45,551 --> 01:11:48,554
AND WHO'S OUT THERE
TRYING TO STOP THEM ?

885
01:11:48,554 --> 01:11:52,558
THE GERMANS !  THEY'RE
NOT YOUR ENEMIES.
THEY'RE YOUR ALLIES !

886
01:11:53,058 --> 01:11:55,060
COMMUNISM IS THE ENEMY
OF ALL OF US !

887
01:11:55,060 --> 01:11:58,564
- I WANT VOLUNTEERS FOR
  THE FREE AMERICAN CORPS.
- [ Lazzaro Coughs ]

888
01:11:59,064 --> 01:12:02,067
-MEN WHO ARE WILLING TO
 STAND UP TO THESE COMMIES.
- SIT DOWN, LAZZARO !

889
01:12:02,067 --> 01:12:05,070
I DIDN'T VOTE FOR YOU,
DERBY.
GOOD.  NOW, WHO'S NEXT ?

890
01:12:05,070 --> 01:12:09,191
-[ Siren ]
-IF WE DON'T STOP THEM--
- EVERYBODY TO THE AIR SHELTER.

891
01:12:09,191 --> 01:12:12,528
MOVE.  LET'S GO !
[ Man ]
GET OUTTA MY WAY.

892
01:12:12,528 --> 01:12:16,031
THERE'LL BE NO BOMBS.
CHURCHILL'S NEPHEW
LIVES IN DRESDEN.

893
01:12:16,031 --> 01:12:20,536
[ Siren Blaring ]

894
01:12:26,041 --> 01:12:30,045
[ Siren Continues ]

895
01:12:40,556 --> 01:12:42,558
DON'T WORRY, SOLDIER.

896
01:12:50,065 --> 01:12:53,068
[ Door Slams Shut ]

897
01:12:53,569 --> 01:12:56,572
WELL, MEN, DO I HAVE
ONLY ONE VOLUNTEER ?

898
01:12:57,072 --> 01:13:01,076
LISTEN, PAL.  I ONLY STOOD UP
BACK THERE TO TELL YOU THAT ONE
DAY YOUR DOORBELL'S GONNA RING,

899
01:13:01,577 --> 01:13:03,579
AND THERE'S GONNA BE THIS GUY
IN A TRENCH COAT--

900
01:13:03,579 --> 01:13:06,582
WE'LL EAT GERMAN CRAW
FOR SO LONG, CAMPBELL,
BECAUSE WE HAVE TO.

901
01:13:06,582 --> 01:13:08,584
BUT WE'D RATHER DIE
THAN EAT YOUR DUNG,

902
01:13:08,584 --> 01:13:11,086
WHICH IS SICK AND LOUSY
AND FOUL !

903
01:13:11,086 --> 01:13:13,088
HISTORY WILL PROVE YOU
AN ASS.

904
01:13:13,088 --> 01:13:16,592
[ Airplane Engines Droning ]

905
01:13:17,593 --> 01:13:20,596
OH, SHIT.

906
01:13:20,596 --> 01:13:23,098
[ Bombs Shrieking ]

907
01:13:23,098 --> 01:13:25,100
NO BOMBS,
EH, CAMPBELL ?

908
01:13:25,100 --> 01:13:27,603
YOU CAN'T TRUST
THE JEWS.

909
01:13:28,604 --> 01:13:33,575
[ Continuous Explosions ]

910
01:14:06,208 --> 01:14:08,610
DADDY, YOU SHOULD REALLY
STAY WITH US.

911
01:14:08,610 --> 01:14:10,612
AND YOU SHOULDN'T TALK
ABOUT MAMA...

912
01:14:11,013 --> 01:14:13,816
OR THE ACCIDENT,
 OR EVEN THE WAR.

913
01:14:13,816 --> 01:14:17,019
I JUST WANNA GO HOME.
BUT WE WANT YOU WITH US !

914
01:14:17,019 --> 01:14:19,421
I'LL BE FINE.
JUST FOR ONE NIGHT ?

915
01:14:19,421 --> 01:14:22,491
NO.
OH, DADDY.  HONESTLY !

916
01:14:40,092 --> 01:14:43,695
DADDY, YOU SHOULD
CONSIDER YOURSELF LUCKY.

917
01:14:43,695 --> 01:14:46,899
PRACTICALLY EVERY OPTOMETRIST
IN ILIUM WAS WIPED OUT.

918
01:14:46,899 --> 01:14:49,401
STANLEY'S BEEN WORKING
NIGHT AND DAY FOR YOU.

919
01:14:49,401 --> 01:14:51,904
STINKING OLD DOG.

920
01:15:03,115 --> 01:15:06,618
HELLO, SPOT.
YEAH.

921
01:15:13,041 --> 01:15:15,043
YEAH.

922
01:15:15,043 --> 01:15:17,045
DADDY, HONESTLY !

923
01:15:21,950 --> 01:15:25,637
WON'T YOU PLEASE CHANGE YOUR
MIND AND COME STAY WITH US ?

924
01:15:26,038 --> 01:15:30,025
YOU'LL BE IN THIS EMPTY HOUSE
WITH THAT OLD DOG.

925
01:15:30,025 --> 01:15:33,529
I'LL BE ALL RIGHT.
BUT, DADDY, BE REALISTIC.

926
01:15:33,529 --> 01:15:37,533
YOU JUST TURNED MIDDLE-AGED.
YOU'VE GOT YOUR WHOLE LIFE
AHEAD OF YOU.

927
01:15:37,533 --> 01:15:40,536
GOOD NIGHT, DEAR.

928
01:17:10,242 --> 01:17:14,246
[ Door Creaks ]

929
01:17:15,747 --> 01:17:19,751
[ Metal Clatters ]

930
01:17:22,254 --> 01:17:26,258
[ Flames Crackling ]

931
01:17:34,266 --> 01:17:35,767
[ Soldier Coughs ]

932
01:17:41,273 --> 01:17:44,276
[ Coughing ]

933
01:18:09,801 --> 01:18:13,805
JA, SCHWEINE !
VERFLUCHEN SCHWEINE !

934
01:18:37,879 --> 01:18:41,883
[ Men Shouting ]

935
01:19:17,686 --> 01:19:20,322
[ Screams ]

936
01:19:22,324 --> 01:19:25,127
MAMA !
 MAMA !

937
01:19:25,127 --> 01:19:28,730
MAMA !  MAMA !

938
01:19:28,730 --> 01:19:31,133
[ Fire Fighters Shouting ]

939
01:19:31,133 --> 01:19:33,135
[ Boy Wailing In German ]

940
01:19:33,135 --> 01:19:37,606
-[ Robert ]  DAD ?  DAD ?
-[ Boy Screaming ]
 PAPA !

941
01:19:40,609 --> 01:19:43,612
DAD ?

942
01:19:43,612 --> 01:19:45,614
ROBERT ?

943
01:19:48,116 --> 01:19:51,620
HIYA, DAD.
HI, SPOT.

944
01:19:53,121 --> 01:19:55,207
HOW DID YOU GET HERE ?

945
01:19:55,607 --> 01:19:58,493
WELL, THEY--
THEY GAVE ME LEAVE
TO VISIT MOM.

946
01:19:58,493 --> 01:20:01,713
[ Sighs ]
BUT YOU KNOW--
SURE, DAD.  I KNOW.

947
01:20:02,113 --> 01:20:05,917
THAT'S WHY I'M HERE.
AND TO SEE YOU.

948
01:20:08,420 --> 01:20:13,024
HOW ARE YOU, DAD ?
I'M FINE.

949
01:20:13,425 --> 01:20:17,712
GOD, DAD.  TO THINK THAT
YOU LIVED.  IT'S A MIRACLE.

950
01:20:17,712 --> 01:20:20,649
LIKE ONE TIME WHEN A CHOPPER
GOT HIT BY CHARLIE,

951
01:20:20,649 --> 01:20:22,651
JUST OUTSIDE OUR CAMP.

952
01:20:23,151 --> 01:20:25,654
IT CAME DOWN LIKE,
LIKE A STONE.

953
01:20:25,654 --> 01:20:28,156
BUT THE DOOR GUNNER
WALKED AWAY.

954
01:20:29,658 --> 01:20:32,661
DAD ?

955
01:20:32,661 --> 01:20:36,164
DAD, I-I DID THE RIGHT
THING, JOINING UP.

956
01:20:36,164 --> 01:20:38,166
I'M SURE YOU DID, SON.

957
01:20:38,667 --> 01:20:43,672
AAH, IT'S A LOUSY WAR, BUT
SOONER OR LATER IT'S GONNA
BE US OR THE COMMUNISTS.

958
01:20:43,672 --> 01:20:45,674
WE'VE GOTTA STAND UP
TO THEM SOMEWHERE.

959
01:20:47,676 --> 01:20:49,678
DAD ?

960
01:20:51,179 --> 01:20:53,181
DAD ?

961
01:20:55,133 --> 01:20:59,337
I KNOW YOU AND MOM
WORRIED ABOUT ME A LOT.

962
01:20:59,337 --> 01:21:01,373
I GUESS I HAVEN'T BEEN
THE BEST OF SONS.

963
01:21:01,773 --> 01:21:05,277
YOU'VE BEEN JUST FINE, ROBERT.
NO, I--  I KNOW
I WAS PRETTY WILD,

964
01:21:05,277 --> 01:21:08,280
AND I WANT TO MAKE UP
FOR IT.

965
01:21:08,280 --> 01:21:11,283
REMEMBER THAT STUFF
IN THE CEMETERY ?  GEEZ !

966
01:21:11,283 --> 01:21:14,286
I'M SO ASHAMED OF THAT NOW.
REALLY, I AM.

967
01:21:15,704 --> 01:21:17,539
BUT I'VE CHANGED
A LOT, DAD.

968
01:21:19,541 --> 01:21:23,278
AND I JUST HOPE I CAN
MAKE YOU REAL PROUD
OF ME FROM NOW ON.

969
01:21:24,713 --> 01:21:26,715
YOU ALREADY HAVE, ROBERT.

970
01:21:30,835 --> 01:21:34,089
DAD, WILL YOU COME
TO MOM'S GRAVE WITH ME ?

971
01:21:35,590 --> 01:21:38,093
I'M NOT READY YET.

972
01:21:38,093 --> 01:21:40,095
I KNOW HOW YOU FEEL, DAD.

973
01:21:46,101 --> 01:21:48,603
I'M JUST NOT READY.

974
01:21:52,107 --> 01:21:54,109
OKAY, DAD.

975
01:23:24,199 --> 01:23:28,703
[ Applause, Cheering ]

976
01:23:28,703 --> 01:23:30,705
WHAT'S HAPPENED ?

977
01:23:30,705 --> 01:23:32,707
[ Cheering Continues ]

978
01:23:33,191 --> 01:23:35,593
WHERE AM I ?

979
01:23:35,593 --> 01:23:38,797
[ Spokesman ]
WELCOME TO THE PLANET
TRALFAMADORE, MR. PILGRIM.

980
01:23:39,197 --> 01:23:41,199
TRALFAM--

981
01:23:41,199 --> 01:23:44,402
TRALFAMA--
TRALFAMADORE.

982
01:23:44,402 --> 01:23:47,355
OH.
[ Spectators Murmuring ]

983
01:23:48,857 --> 01:23:53,278
HOW DID I GET HERE ?
THERE IS NO "HOW," MR. PILGRIM.
 THERE IS NO WHY.

984
01:23:53,278 --> 01:23:56,081
THE MOMENT SIMPLY IS.

985
01:23:57,565 --> 01:24:00,068
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

986
01:24:00,068 --> 01:24:04,072
WHERE ARE YOU ?
OH, YOU CAN'T SEE US,
MR. PILGRIM.

987
01:24:04,072 --> 01:24:07,575
WE LIVE IN THE FOURTH DIMENSION.
BUT WE CAN SEE YOU,

988
01:24:07,575 --> 01:24:11,579
AND THERE ARE MANY
IMPORTANT TRALFAMADORIANS
HERE TO WELCOME YOU.

989
01:24:11,579 --> 01:24:16,584
OH.  WELL, UH,
HOW DO YOU DO ?

990
01:24:16,584 --> 01:24:20,288
WE HOPE THAT YOU'LL FIND YOUR
ACCOMMODATIONS HERE SUITABLE.

991
01:24:20,288 --> 01:24:22,690
I HAVE TO STAY HERE ?

992
01:24:23,091 --> 01:24:25,493
I'M AFRAID SO.

993
01:24:25,493 --> 01:24:29,497
YOU MEAN, I CAN'T LEAVE
OF MY OWN FREE WILL ?

994
01:24:29,497 --> 01:24:34,702
MR. PILGRIM, WE HAVE VISITED
31 INHABITED PLANETS
IN THE UNIVERSE.

995
01:24:34,702 --> 01:24:37,906
WE HAVE STUDIED REPORTS
ON A HUNDRED MORE,

996
01:24:37,906 --> 01:24:42,710
AND ONLY ON EARTH
IS THERE ANY TALK OF FREE WILL.

997
01:24:45,914 --> 01:24:48,733
WELL--
WHAT'LL I DO ?

998
01:24:52,237 --> 01:24:56,641
[ German Officer ]
YOU WILL AID IN THE REMOVAL
OF THE BODIES.

999
01:24:56,641 --> 01:24:59,594
THOSE THAT ARE IDENTIFIABLE...

1000
01:24:59,594 --> 01:25:01,596
WILL BE TAGGED.

1001
01:25:01,596 --> 01:25:06,601
THEIR PERSONAL EFFECTS WILL BE
TAGGED AND GIVEN TO AN OFFICER.

1002
01:25:06,601 --> 01:25:09,104
THERE WILL BE
A CLASSIFICATION...

1003
01:25:09,604 --> 01:25:11,106
ACCORDING TO THE DEGREE...

1004
01:25:11,606 --> 01:25:14,109
THAT THE VICTIM
CAN BE IDENTIFIED.

1005
01:25:14,109 --> 01:25:16,611
ANY LOOTING OR STEALING...

1006
01:25:16,611 --> 01:25:18,613
WILL BE DEALT WITH
BY A FIRING SQUAD.

1007
01:25:19,114 --> 01:25:20,615
FOLLOW ME.

1008
01:25:48,259 --> 01:25:50,762
[ Billy ]
IT LOOKED LIKE
THE END OF THE WORLD.

1009
01:25:50,762 --> 01:25:53,264
[ Spokesman ]
WHAT LOOKED LIKE THE END
OF THE WORLD, MR. PILGRIM ?

1010
01:25:53,765 --> 01:25:55,767
[ Billy ]
DRESDEN, AFTER THE BOMBING.

1011
01:25:55,767 --> 01:25:58,269
[ Spokesman ]
DON'T BE SO EGOCENTRIC.

1012
01:25:58,770 --> 01:26:01,906
WE KNOW HOW THE WORLD ENDS,
AND IT HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH EARTH,

1013
01:26:01,906 --> 01:26:04,108
EXCEPT THAT IT
GETS WIPED OUT TOO.

1014
01:26:04,108 --> 01:26:07,111
[ Billy ]
REALLY ?  HOW DOES IT END ?

1015
01:26:07,111 --> 01:26:09,614
[ Spokesman ]
WHILE WE'RE EXPERIMENTING
WITH NEW FUELS,

1016
01:26:09,614 --> 01:26:14,118
A TRALFAMADORIAN TEST PILOT
PANICS, PRESSES
THE WRONG BUTTON,

1017
01:26:14,118 --> 01:26:16,120
AND THE WHOLE UNIVERSE
DISAPPEARS.

1018
01:26:16,120 --> 01:26:18,623
[ Billy ]
BUT YOU HAVE TO STOP HIM !

1019
01:26:18,623 --> 01:26:21,292
IF YOU KNOW THIS, CAN'T YOU KEEP
THE PILOT FROM PRESSING--

1020
01:26:21,292 --> 01:26:24,896
[ Spokesman ]
HE HAS ALWAYS PRESSED IT,
AND HE ALWAYS WILL.

1021
01:26:24,896 --> 01:26:28,499
WE ALWAYS LET HIM,
AND WE ALWAYS WILL LET HIM.

1022
01:26:28,499 --> 01:26:30,501
THE MOMENT IS STRUCTURED
THAT WAY.

1023
01:27:09,107 --> 01:27:13,094
[ Spokesman ]
MR. PILGRIM, A PLEASANT WAY
TO SPEND ETERNITY...

1024
01:27:13,094 --> 01:27:18,049
IS TO IGNORE THE BAD TIMES
AND CONCENTRATE ON THE GOOD.

1025
01:27:18,416 --> 01:27:22,904
[ Spectators Exclaiming ]

1026
01:27:22,904 --> 01:27:26,991
- [ Screaming ]
-[ Spectators Applaud, Cheer ]

1027
01:27:27,475 --> 01:27:30,278
[ Screaming ]
IT'S-- IT'S ALL RIGHT !
 IT'S ALL RIGHT !

1028
01:27:30,278 --> 01:27:33,481
WILL YOU BE QUIET, PLEASE ?
 WILL YOU PLEASE BE QUIET ?

1029
01:27:33,481 --> 01:27:35,750
CAN'T YOU SEE
YOU'RE FRIGHTENING HER ?

1030
01:27:36,167 --> 01:27:38,469
-[ Spectators Gasp,
   Spot Barks ]
- WHO ARE YOU ?

1031
01:27:38,469 --> 01:27:40,421
[ Barking ]
WHO ARE YOU ?

1032
01:27:40,421 --> 01:27:43,925
[ Choking ]
MY NAME'S PILGRIM.
WHAT'S THIS SCENE ?

1033
01:27:43,925 --> 01:27:47,929
- WHERE ARE WE ?
- [ Gasping ]  WE'RE ON
  A DISTANT PLANET.

1034
01:27:47,929 --> 01:27:49,931
[ Spokesman ]
ARE YOU MATING NOW ?

1035
01:27:49,931 --> 01:27:51,933
[ Panting ]

1036
01:27:52,417 --> 01:27:56,020
WHAT ?
HAVE YOU MATED ?

1037
01:27:58,523 --> 01:28:00,525
WHO ARE YOU ?

1038
01:28:00,525 --> 01:28:03,528
I'M A TRALFAMADORIAN,
MISS WILDHACK.

1039
01:28:05,530 --> 01:28:09,167
A WHAT ?
YOU'RE ON THE PLANET
TRALFAMADORE, MISS WILDHACK,

1040
01:28:09,167 --> 01:28:12,954
423 BILLION MILES FROM EARTH.

1041
01:28:12,954 --> 01:28:14,956
OH, JESUS.

1042
01:28:19,193 --> 01:28:23,598
[ Whispering ]
HEY, HEY.  HEY.

1043
01:28:25,199 --> 01:28:27,602
[ Grunts ]

1044
01:28:28,403 --> 01:28:31,556
YOU'RE OKAY ?
YES, THANK YOU.

1045
01:28:31,556 --> 01:28:34,559
WHEN WERE YOU BORN ?
WHAT MONTH ?
WHAT MONTH ?

1046
01:28:34,559 --> 01:28:37,562
WHAT MONTH ?
JULY.

1047
01:28:37,562 --> 01:28:40,565
WHAT DAY ?
THE FOURTH.
 THE FOURTH OF JULY.

1048
01:28:41,065 --> 01:28:43,067
YOU'RE PRACTICAL,
STRAIGHTFORWARD,
WITH A BELIEF IN OTHERS...

1049
01:28:43,067 --> 01:28:47,071
BASED ON YOUR OWN INTEGRITY
AND ALMOST COMPULSIVE HONESTY.

1050
01:28:48,573 --> 01:28:51,075
YOU'RE A MOON CHILD !

1051
01:28:51,576 --> 01:28:54,078
OH, YOU'RE A MOON CHILD.
I'M A WHAT ?

1052
01:28:54,078 --> 01:28:57,582
A MOON CHILD.  THAT'S YOUR SIGN.

1053
01:28:57,582 --> 01:29:02,587
WERE YOU BORN IN THE MORNING
OR THE AFTERNOON ?  IT DOESN'T
MATTER.  I DON'T HAVE MY CHARTS.

1054
01:29:02,587 --> 01:29:06,090
MISS WILDHACK ?  WOULD YOU
LIKE SOMETHING TO WEAR ?

1055
01:29:06,591 --> 01:29:10,094
OH, YES.
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

1056
01:29:10,094 --> 01:29:14,148
UM--
I WAS, UH--

1057
01:29:14,148 --> 01:29:18,970
I WAS DOWN IN PALM SPRINGS
AT A HOME OF A PRODUCER
FRIEND OF MINE,

1058
01:29:18,970 --> 01:29:21,439
SUNNING MYSELF
BY THE POOL.

1059
01:29:21,439 --> 01:29:24,442
THAT'S WHY I'M LIKE THIS.
I DON'T WANT HALTER MARKS.

1060
01:29:24,442 --> 01:29:27,945
NATURALLY.  AND...

1061
01:29:27,945 --> 01:29:31,949
ALL OF A SUDDEN,
IT WAS LIKE A-- A RAY--

1062
01:29:31,949 --> 01:29:34,452
THIS IS ALL
I CAN OFFER.
THANK YOU.

1063
01:29:34,452 --> 01:29:38,990
AND--
I'M SORRY.  I DIDN'T
MEAN TO INTERRUPT.

1064
01:29:38,990 --> 01:29:42,193
TH-THAT'S ALL THERE IS.
AND THE NEXT THING,
I WAS--

1065
01:29:42,193 --> 01:29:46,564
I WAS HERE.
WHAT'S IT LIKE UP HERE ?

1066
01:29:46,564 --> 01:29:49,000
I DON'T KNOW.
WE CAN'T LEAVE THE DOME.

1067
01:29:49,000 --> 01:29:52,503
[ Spokesman ]
THE ATMOSPHERE OF TRALFAMADORE
IS CYANIDE.

1068
01:29:52,503 --> 01:29:55,506
IT WOULD BE FATAL TO YOU
IF YOU LEFT THE DOME.

1069
01:29:56,007 --> 01:29:57,508
THIS IS IT ?

1070
01:29:58,009 --> 01:30:01,512
I'M... AFRAID SO.

1071
01:30:01,512 --> 01:30:04,682
HOW LONG WILL THEY
KEEP US HERE ?
I DON'T KNOW.

1072
01:30:04,682 --> 01:30:08,403
[ Spokesman ]
YOU ARE HERE,
YOU HAVE ALWAYS BEEN HERE,

1073
01:30:08,403 --> 01:30:11,406
AND YOU WILL
ALWAYS BE HERE.

1074
01:30:13,408 --> 01:30:16,411
IS HE TRYING TO BLOW
MY MIND ?

1075
01:30:16,411 --> 01:30:18,413
NO, NO, NO.
IT ALL MAKES SENSE IN A WAY.

1076
01:30:18,413 --> 01:30:21,916
YOU SEE, IN TRALFAMADORE--
[ Spokesman ]
WOULD YOU PLEASE MATE NOW ?

1077
01:30:25,553 --> 01:30:29,557
LOOK.  WE'RE NOT GOING
TO PUT ON A SHOW FOR YOU.
THAT'S ONE THING.

1078
01:30:29,957 --> 01:30:32,360
ANOTHER IS I DEMAND YOU GET
MISS WILDHACK SOME CLOTHING.

1079
01:30:32,360 --> 01:30:35,296
[ Spokesman ]
IF SHE'S COLD, WE CAN ALWAYS
REGULATE THE TEMPERATURE.

1080
01:30:35,296 --> 01:30:37,515
NOW, YOU GET DOWN TO EARTH
AND GET MISS WILDHACK...

1081
01:30:37,515 --> 01:30:39,517
A COMPLETE WARDROBE,
AND ONE THAT FITS !

1082
01:30:39,917 --> 01:30:42,687
WHAT'S YOUR SIZE ?
I TAKE A TEN.

1083
01:30:42,687 --> 01:30:46,691
BUT I HAVE TO TAKE IT IN HERE
AND LET IT OUT A LITTLE HERE.

1084
01:30:46,691 --> 01:30:50,194
SO, THEY'LL HAVE TO BRING
A NEEDLE AND THREAD.
DID YOU HEAR THAT ?

1085
01:30:50,194 --> 01:30:53,197
AND REMEMBER, MISS WILDHACK
IS USED TO THE BEST.

1086
01:30:53,197 --> 01:30:55,199
THANKS !  UH--

1087
01:30:55,199 --> 01:30:58,703
- BILLY.
- BILLY.

1088
01:31:07,411 --> 01:31:09,914
NOW WE WOULD LIKE
THE NIGHT CANOPY.

1089
01:31:09,914 --> 01:31:11,916
[ Spokesman ]
WHY DO YOU WISH
THE NIGHT CANOPY ?

1090
01:31:11,916 --> 01:31:14,418
[ Billy ]
BECAUSE WE WANT IT !
WILL YOU MATE ?

1091
01:31:14,418 --> 01:31:17,905
WE HARDLY KNOW EACH OTHER !
DO YOU MIND IF WE TAKE TIME
TO GET BETTER ACQUAINTED ?

1092
01:31:18,306 --> 01:31:20,708
[ Spokesman ]
YOU ARE ACTING VERY UNNATURALLY.

1093
01:31:21,108 --> 01:31:24,312
WE WOULD LIKE
THE NIGHT CANOPY.

1094
01:31:24,312 --> 01:31:27,815
[ Spokesman ]
OH, VERY WELL.
[ Spectators Groan ]

1095
01:31:30,818 --> 01:31:33,321
WOULD YOU LIKE TO SIT
ON THE COUCH ?

1096
01:31:34,822 --> 01:31:38,826
WHERE IS IT ?
HERE.  JUST TAKE MY HAND.

1097
01:31:38,826 --> 01:31:40,828
OOH !
OOH !  I'M SORRY.

1098
01:31:41,329 --> 01:31:43,831
UM, THAT'S ALL RIGHT.

1099
01:31:48,336 --> 01:31:51,839
CAREFUL.
GET AWAY, SPOT.

1100
01:31:53,341 --> 01:31:56,344
HE'S NOT BOTHERING ME.
I LIKE DOGS.

1101
01:31:56,344 --> 01:31:58,346
COME HERE, SPOT.
 COME ON.

1102
01:31:59,847 --> 01:32:02,850
IT'S PRETTY COMFORTABLE,
ISN'T IT ?
IT'S FINE.

1103
01:32:02,850 --> 01:32:05,853
THEY GOT EVERYTHING
FROM SEARS AND ROEBUCK.

1104
01:32:05,853 --> 01:32:09,857
I APPRECIATE WHAT YOU SAID
TO THEM ABOUT ME.

1105
01:32:09,857 --> 01:32:13,361
THANK YOU,
MISS WILDHACK.
MONTANA.

1106
01:32:13,361 --> 01:32:16,364
MONTANA.
YOU DON'T MEET
MANY GENTLEMEN...

1107
01:32:16,364 --> 01:32:18,866
IN THE ENTERTAINMENT
BUSINESS.

1108
01:32:18,866 --> 01:32:21,869
I'M AN OPTOMETRIST.
OH.

1109
01:32:21,869 --> 01:32:23,871
WOULD YOU LIKE
TO KISS ME ?

1110
01:32:23,871 --> 01:32:25,873
YES.

1111
01:32:28,876 --> 01:32:31,379
YOU KISS NICELY.

1112
01:32:31,379 --> 01:32:33,881
THANK YOU.
OH !  DID I HURT YOU ?

1113
01:32:34,382 --> 01:32:37,385
OH, NO !
 OH !

1114
01:32:39,387 --> 01:32:41,389
[ Spokesman ]
MR. PILGRIM ?

1115
01:32:43,391 --> 01:32:44,892
MISS WILDHACK ?

1116
01:32:47,395 --> 01:32:49,397
ARE YOU MATING NOW ?

1117
01:33:06,447 --> 01:33:08,449
BILLY !

1118
01:33:08,950 --> 01:33:11,452
BILLY, LOOK AT THIS !

1119
01:33:11,452 --> 01:33:15,456
LOOK AT THIS !
PERFECT.  THERE'S
NOT A CHIP ON IT.

1120
01:33:15,456 --> 01:33:18,459
IT'S EXACTLY LIKE THE ONE
WE HAD AT HOME.
THE ONE YOUR SON JOHNNY BROKE ?

1121
01:33:18,459 --> 01:33:21,462
YEAH !  HOW'D YOU
KNOW ABOUT THAT ?

1122
01:33:21,462 --> 01:33:25,466
THE LETTER YOU WROTE HOME.
OF COURSE.  IT'S
A MIRACLE, ISN'T IT ?

1123
01:33:25,466 --> 01:33:29,971
THIS LITTLE DANCER SURVIVED
ALL THIS DESTRUCTION.

1124
01:33:29,971 --> 01:33:33,474
WAIT'LL I BRING IT HOME.
CAN YOU IMAGINE HOW
MEG'S EYES WILL LIGHT UP ?

1125
01:33:33,474 --> 01:33:35,476
[ Guard ]
ARBEIT !
SHE'LL LOVE IT.

1126
01:33:35,476 --> 01:33:38,479
[ Man ]
 DIENER ?

1127
01:33:38,479 --> 01:33:40,281
WAS HABEN SIE DA ?

1128
01:33:40,281 --> 01:33:44,285
OH, UH, LOOK AT THIS.

1129
01:33:44,785 --> 01:33:47,872
I FOUND THIS DOWN THERE.
THERE'S NOT A CHIP ON IT.
IT'S PRETTY, ISN'T IT ?

1130
01:33:47,872 --> 01:33:51,876
WE HAD ONE LIKE IT.
USED TO SIT--  OH !
[ Speaking German ]

1131
01:33:51,876 --> 01:33:55,830
[ Derby ]
WHAT'S THE MATTER ?
[ Speaking German ]

1132
01:33:57,832 --> 01:34:02,837
[ Conversing In German ]

1133
01:34:06,841 --> 01:34:10,344
[ Officer ]
FEUER !
[ Gunshots ]

1134
01:34:12,146 --> 01:34:15,249
[ Billy ]
STOP !  STOP !

1135
01:34:25,743 --> 01:34:29,747
BILLY.  BILLY ?
 BILLY ?

1136
01:34:31,749 --> 01:34:34,251
WHERE WERE YOU, HONEY ?

1137
01:34:38,255 --> 01:34:40,758
BILLY ?  DO YOU LIKE THIS ?

1138
01:34:46,263 --> 01:34:49,767
- IT'S NICE.
- IT'S, UH, NOT TOO TIGHT ?

1139
01:34:49,767 --> 01:34:53,771
[ Chuckles ]
A LITTLE, MAYBE.

1140
01:34:53,771 --> 01:34:55,773
I'M SO BIG HERE.

1141
01:34:55,773 --> 01:34:58,776
I LIKE IT.

1142
01:34:58,776 --> 01:35:01,278
THAT'S 'CAUSE YOU'RE A MAN.

1143
01:35:02,780 --> 01:35:05,783
- I'M GONNA
  HAVE TO LET IT OUT.
- I REALLY THINK--

1144
01:35:05,783 --> 01:35:08,285
GIVE ME SOMETHING TO DO.
[ Spot Growls ]

1145
01:35:10,287 --> 01:35:12,289
OH.  YOU LIKE IT TOO,
SPOT.  HUH ?

1146
01:35:12,790 --> 01:35:15,292
HE ALWAYS GROWLED
AT MY WIFE.

1147
01:35:16,293 --> 01:35:19,296
DO YOU MISS HER ?

1148
01:35:22,299 --> 01:35:25,803
SHE DIED.  SOMEBODY SMACKED
INTO THE REAR OF HER CAR...

1149
01:35:25,803 --> 01:35:28,305
AND THE EXHAUST FELL OFF.

1150
01:35:28,305 --> 01:35:30,307
SHE DIED OF CARBON MONOXIDE
POISONING.

1151
01:35:30,808 --> 01:35:34,311
OH.  LIKE WHAT
THEY HAVE OUT THERE ?

1152
01:35:34,311 --> 01:35:37,314
NO.  THAT'S CYANIDE.
THAT'S WORSE.

1153
01:35:37,314 --> 01:35:39,316
OH, WOW.

1154
01:35:40,818 --> 01:35:42,820
WHAT DID YOU LOVE MOST
ABOUT HER ?

1155
01:35:48,325 --> 01:35:51,328
HER PANCAKES.

1156
01:35:52,830 --> 01:35:55,833
IF WE HAD A REAL STOVE,
BILLY,

1157
01:35:55,833 --> 01:35:58,836
I'D MAKE YOU AN OUT-OF-SIGHT
MACROBIOTIC SOUFFLE.

1158
01:35:58,836 --> 01:36:01,839
[ Chuckles ]
I'D LIKE THAT.

1159
01:36:01,839 --> 01:36:04,842
AND THEN...

1160
01:36:04,842 --> 01:36:07,845
WE COULD THINK
ABOUT HAVING YOUR BABY.

1161
01:36:13,851 --> 01:36:16,854
COULD WE HAVE
THE NIGHT CANOPY, PLEASE ?

1162
01:36:20,858 --> 01:36:22,860
[ Sighs ]

1163
01:36:24,361 --> 01:36:28,365
OH, DADDY !
THERE IS NO SUCH PLANET
AS TRILAFLAMADUKE !

1164
01:36:28,365 --> 01:36:32,386
DAD, I THINK WHAT
BARBARA AND I WOULD
REALLY LIKE TO KNOW--

1165
01:36:32,386 --> 01:36:34,321
WOULD YOU BE WILLING
TO SEE A PSYCHIATRIST ?

1166
01:36:34,822 --> 01:36:38,425
LISTEN, I HAVE A FRIEND
WHO'S NOT ONLY A DOCTOR,

1167
01:36:38,425 --> 01:36:40,427
BUT HE'S INTERESTED
IN OUTER SPACE.

1168
01:36:40,427 --> 01:36:43,414
WHY DON'T THE THREE OF US
HAVE LUNCH TOGETHER TODAY ?

1169
01:36:43,414 --> 01:36:46,250
I'M NOT GOING TO COMMIT
MYSELF TO AN INSTITUTION.
DAD, I WASN'T--

1170
01:36:46,250 --> 01:36:50,421
IF IT WEREN'T FOR TRALFAMADORE,
I MIGHT HAVE NEEDED
AN INSTITUTION.

1171
01:36:52,089 --> 01:36:54,892
I DON'T NEED A DOCTOR, STANLEY.

1172
01:36:54,892 --> 01:36:56,894
ON TRALFAMADORE YOU LEARN
THAT THE WORLD...

1173
01:36:56,894 --> 01:37:01,699
IS JUST A COLLECTION OF
MOMENTS ALL STRUNG TOGETHER
IN BEAUTIFUL, RANDOM ORDER.

1174
01:37:02,099 --> 01:37:06,353
AND IF WE'RE GOING TO SURVIVE,
IT'S UP TO US TO CONCENTRATE
ON THE GOOD MOMENTS...

1175
01:37:06,353 --> 01:37:08,589
AND IGNORE THE BAD.

1176
01:37:08,589 --> 01:37:10,591
BESIDES, I'M IN LOVE UP THERE.

1177
01:37:10,591 --> 01:37:13,994
YOU KNOW, DAD, I'D REALLY LIKE
TO HAVE LUNCH WITH YOU TODAY.

1178
01:37:13,994 --> 01:37:16,831
I'LL BE VERY BUSY.

1179
01:37:18,032 --> 01:37:20,034
MONTANA'S PREGNANT.

1180
01:37:22,636 --> 01:37:25,039
WHAT'S HER NAME ?

1181
01:37:25,039 --> 01:37:26,924
MONTANA WILDHACK.

1182
01:37:26,924 --> 01:37:29,877
THAT'S THE HOLLYWOOD STARLET
WHO DISAPPEARED, ISN'T IT ?

1183
01:37:29,877 --> 01:37:32,363
OH, MY GOD.

1184
01:37:32,363 --> 01:37:36,016
DAD !  HEY, W-WAIT
A MINUTE, DAD.

1185
01:37:36,016 --> 01:37:38,135
DAD, LISTEN.

1186
01:37:38,135 --> 01:37:41,639
I-IF YOU GO BACK AND FORTH
IN TIME, DO YOU GO
INTO THE FUTURE TOO ?

1187
01:37:41,639 --> 01:37:44,642
- MM-HMM.  FREQUENTLY.
- WELL--

1188
01:37:44,642 --> 01:37:47,144
I MEAN, H-HOW FAR
DO YOU GO ?

1189
01:37:47,144 --> 01:37:52,149
- DO YOU ACTUALLY GO--
- ALL THE WAY TO MY DEATH.
  I'VE SEEN IT MANY TIMES.

1190
01:37:52,149 --> 01:37:56,654
I DIED IN PHILADELPHIA,
WHERE I WAS GIVING A SPEECH
ON THE SUBJECT OF TRALFAMADORE.

1191
01:37:57,154 --> 01:38:01,659
YOU SEE, IN TRALFAMADORE,
WHERE I PRESENTLY DWELL,

1192
01:38:01,659 --> 01:38:03,661
LIFE HAS NO BEGINNING,

1193
01:38:03,661 --> 01:38:07,665
NO MIDDLE AND NO END.

1194
01:38:07,665 --> 01:38:09,667
FOR EXAMPLE,
MANY YEARS AGO...

1195
01:38:10,167 --> 01:38:13,170
A CERTAIN MAN PROMISED
TO HAVE ME KILLED.

1196
01:38:13,170 --> 01:38:17,675
HE'S AN OLD MAN NOW,
LIVING NOT FAR FROM HERE.

1197
01:38:18,175 --> 01:38:22,179
HE'S READ ALL OF THE PUBLICITY
ASSOCIATED WITH MY APPEARANCE.

1198
01:38:22,179 --> 01:38:25,683
HE'S INSANE, AND TONIGHT
HE'LL KEEP HIS PROMISE.

1199
01:38:26,183 --> 01:38:28,185
[ Audience Murmuring,
  Protesting ]

1200
01:38:31,188 --> 01:38:33,190
[ Murmuring Subsides ]

1201
01:38:33,190 --> 01:38:35,192
IF YOU PROTEST,

1202
01:38:35,693 --> 01:38:38,195
IF YOU THINK THAT DEATH
IS A TERRIBLE THING,

1203
01:38:38,195 --> 01:38:42,199
THEN YOU HAVE NOT UNDERSTOOD
WHAT I HAVE SAID.

1204
01:38:42,199 --> 01:38:44,702
YOU SEE, IT'S TIME
FOR YOU TO GO HOME...

1205
01:38:44,702 --> 01:38:47,705
TO YOUR WIVES AND CHILDREN.

1206
01:38:48,205 --> 01:38:51,709
IT'S TIME FOR ME TO BE DEAD
FOR A LITTLE WHILE...

1207
01:38:52,209 --> 01:38:54,211
AND THEN LIVE AGAIN.

1208
01:38:54,211 --> 01:38:58,716
[ Murmuring ]
I GIVE YOU
THE TRALFAMADORIAN GREETING:

1209
01:39:01,218 --> 01:39:04,221
"HELLO.  FAREWELL.

1210
01:39:06,223 --> 01:39:08,726
"HELLO.

1211
01:39:09,226 --> 01:39:11,228
"FAREWELL.

1212
01:39:11,729 --> 01:39:14,231
"ETERNALLY CONNECTED,

1213
01:39:14,231 --> 01:39:17,234
"ETERNALLY EMBRACING.

1214
01:39:17,234 --> 01:39:19,737
"HELLO.

1215
01:39:21,238 --> 01:39:24,742
- FAREWELL."
- [ Audience Screaming ]

1216
01:39:26,744 --> 01:39:29,747
NOBODY FUCKS AROUND
WITH PAUL LAZZARO !

1217
01:39:29,747 --> 01:39:32,466
DO YOU HEAR ME,
PILGRIM ?

1218
01:39:32,466 --> 01:39:35,252
PILGRIM ?

1219
01:39:35,252 --> 01:39:37,755
PILGRIM ?

1220
01:39:37,755 --> 01:39:39,757
HEY, PILGRIM !
YOU HEAR ME ?

1221
01:39:40,224 --> 01:39:44,812
PILGRIM, GET YOUR ASS OVER HERE
AND GIVE ME A HAND !

1222
01:39:44,812 --> 01:39:48,032
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA
DO WITH THAT ?
I'M GONNA MAKE A FORTUNE !

1223
01:39:48,032 --> 01:39:49,984
ARE YOU KIDDING ?
[ Grunts ]

1224
01:39:49,984 --> 01:39:52,987
HAVEN'T YOU GOT
ENOUGH STUFF ?
WHAT IF WE GET CAUGHT ?

1225
01:39:52,987 --> 01:39:55,489
WE AIN'T GONNA GET CAUGHT.
THE KRAUTS HAVE ALL LEFT.

1226
01:39:55,990 --> 01:39:59,443
IF WE DON'T STEAL IT,
THE RUSSIANS WILL.
[ Machine Guns Firing ]

1227
01:39:59,443 --> 01:40:02,863
LET'S GET THE FUCK
OUTTA HERE !
WAIT !

1228
01:40:02,863 --> 01:40:05,866
WAIT !  WAIT !
 WAIT !  WAIT !

1229
01:40:07,868 --> 01:40:11,939
[ Pistols Firing,
  Shouting In Russian Language ]

1230
01:40:14,508 --> 01:40:16,627
I SURRENDER !
 I SURRENDER !

1231
01:40:16,627 --> 01:40:20,347
I SURRENDER !

1232
01:40:20,347 --> 01:40:22,383
[ Shouting In Russian ]
I SURRENDER !

1233
01:40:29,790 --> 01:40:32,693
[ Shouting In Russian ]
I DON'T KNOW.

1234
01:40:42,036 --> 01:40:45,205
[ Machine Guns Firing ]

1235
01:40:51,612 --> 01:40:54,848
[ Montana ]
BILLY ?  BILLY ?

1236
01:40:54,848 --> 01:40:56,850
WE JUST HAD A BABY !

1237
01:40:56,850 --> 01:41:00,637
[ Baby Crying ]

1238
01:41:02,639 --> 01:41:06,643
BILLY.  WE'VE JUST HAD
A BABY BOY !

1239
01:41:07,144 --> 01:41:09,146
LOOK AT HIM !
[ Cooing ]

1240
01:41:09,146 --> 01:41:11,148
ISN'T HE BEAUTIFUL ?

1241
01:41:11,648 --> 01:41:14,151
AHH.  YES.
ISN'T HE INCREDIBLY
BEAUTIFUL ?

1242
01:41:14,151 --> 01:41:16,653
HE'S PERFECT.
EVERY BIT OF HIM.
[ Laughs ]

1243
01:41:18,655 --> 01:41:21,658
WHAT SHALL WE CALL HIM ?
BILLY, OF COURSE.

1244
01:41:22,159 --> 01:41:25,662
ANYWAY, EVEN IF HE DOESN'T
LOOK TOO MUCH LIKE YOU,
